  "title": "Pet Collecting",
  "description": "🐶 Relay Mod: Collect various pets with unique abilities by completing actions in-game.",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Various collectable pets are added to the game. During in-game tasks such as chopping wood, swimming and killing monsters they can be added to the player's inventory. Each pet has a unique ability!<br /><br />Pet Collecting was made via the Relay modding principle. Each participant had 4 hours to complete their part of the code, before it was send to the next person. The time limit comes with challenges! Everyone has their own programming style and strengths. With it being relayed 5 times, the initial mod took 20 hours to complete. There will be mod updates in the future.</span><br /><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>There are currently 14 pets added to the game:</strong></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/all_pets.png\" /><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><em>See below for an example on what each pet does, and how to encounter them:</em></span><br /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>The Air Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by flying with an elytra.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/air_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>The Animal Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by slaying animals.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/animal_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>The Dirt Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by digging dirt blocks.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/dirt_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>The End Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by slaying the End Dragon.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/end_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>The Grass Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by walking through tall grass.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/grass_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>The Lava Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by swimming in lava.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/lava_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Monster Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by slaying hostile mobs.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/monster_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Petal Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by breaking flowers.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/petal_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Player Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by player deaths.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/player_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Potion Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by brewing potions.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/potion_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Sand Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by digging sand.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/sand_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Stone Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by breaking stone-type blocks.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/stone_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Water Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by swimming in water.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/water_pet.png\" /><br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Wood Pet</strong></span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><em>Can be encountered by chopping down trees.</em></span><br /><img src=\"https://github.com/relaymodding/Relay-CDN/raw/main/images/pet-collecting/pets/wood_pet.png\" /></p>",
